681702,131,758,77,102,1,143,20,"‘‘ ayaṃ mama kāraṇā evarūpāya iddhiyā parihīno, na dāni yuttaṃ pariccajitun’’ ti idheva tiṭṭhāti vatvā gharaṃ gantvā mātāpitūnaṃ taṃ pavattiṃ ārocesi. "
681703,131,758,103,110,1,62,7,Tepi āgantvā nānappakāraṃ ovadamānā vacanaṃ aggaṇhantaṃ āhaṃsu–
681704,131,758,111,120,1,47,6,"‘‘ tvaṃ amhe uccakulāti sallakkhesi, mayaṃ pesakārā. "
681705,131,758,121,129,1,48,6,Sakkhissasi pesakārakammaṃ kātun’’ ti sāmaṇero āha–
681706,131,758,130,149,1,108,14,"‘‘ upāsaka gihibhūto nāma pesakārakammaṃ vā kareyya naḷakārakammaṃ vā, kiṃ iminā sāṭakamattena lobhaṃ karothā’’ ti. "
681707,131,758,150,158,1,62,8,Pesakāro udare baddhasāṭakaṃ datvā gharaṃ netvā dhītaraṃ adāsi. 
681708,131,759,2,10,1,68,8,So pesakārakammaṃ uggaṇhitvā pesakārehi saddhiṃ sālāya kammaṃ karoti. 
681709,131,759,11,23,1,82,11,"Aññesaṃ itthiyo pātova bhattaṃ sampādetvā āhariṃsu, tassa bhariyā na tāva āgacchati. "
681710,131,759,24,32,1,66,8,So itaresu kammaṃ vissajjetvā bhuñjamānesu tasaraṃ vaṭṭento nisīdi. 
681711,131,759,33,36,1,17,3,Sā pacchā agamāsi. 
681712,131,759,37,49,1,40,7,Atha naṃ so‘‘ aticirena āgatāsī’’ ti tajjesi. 
681713,131,759,50,61,1,91,11,Mātugāmo ca nāma api cakkavattirājānaṃ attani paṭibaddhacittaṃ ñatvā dāsaṃ viya sallakkheti. 
