682095,131,824,23,37,1,85,11,"‘‘ mayaṃ sattānaṃ ekantasukhaṃ vadāma, paṭipadaṃ pana kālena sukhaṃ kālena dukkhaṃ vadāma. "
682096,131,824,38,45,1,69,7,Ekantasukhassa kho pana attano paṭipadāyapi ekantasukhāya bhavitabbaṃ. 
