682099,131,825,2,11,1,52,7,Ettha mayaṃ {anassāmā}ti etasmiṃ kāraṇe mayaṃ anassāma. 
682100,131,825,12,15,1,21,3,Kasmā pana evamāhaṃsu? 
682101,131,825,16,45,1,253,26,"Te kira pubbe pañcasu dhammesu patiṭṭhāya kasiṇaparikammaṃ katvā tatiyajjhānaṃ nibbattetvā aparihīnajjhānā kālaṃ katvā subhakiṇhesu nibbattantīti jānanti, gacchante gacchante pana kāle kasiṇaparikammampi na jāniṃsu, tatiyajjhānampi nibbattetuṃ nāsakkhiṃsu. "
682102,131,825,46,66,1,104,12,Pañca pubbabhāgadhamme pana‘‘ ākāravatī paṭipadā’’ ti uggahetvā tatiyajjhānaṃ‘‘ ekantasukho loko’’ ti uggaṇhiṃsu. 
682103,131,825,67,69,1,16,2,Tasmā evamāhaṃsu. 
