686875,132,430,2,4,1,23,2,1 . Cūḷasuññatasuttavaṇṇanā 
686876,132,431,2,13,1,34,5,176. Evaṃ me sutan ti cūḷasuññatasuttaṃ. 
686877,132,431,14,33,1,182,19,Tattha ekamidan ti thero kira bhagavato vattaṃ katvā attano divāṭṭhānaṃ gantvā kālaparicchedaṃ katvā nibbānārammaṇaṃ suññatāphalasamāpattiṃ appetvā nisinno yathāparicchedena vuṭṭhāsi. 
686878,132,431,34,38,1,37,4,Athassa saṅkhārā suññato upaṭṭhahiṃsu. 
686879,132,431,39,43,1,30,4,So suññatākathaṃ sotukāmo jāto. 
686880,132,431,44,47,1,17,2,Athassa etadahosi –
686881,132,431,48,97,1,279,38,"‘‘ na kho pana sakkā dhurena dhuraṃ paharantena viya gantvā‘ suññatākathaṃ me, bhante, kathethā’ ti bhagavantaṃ vattuṃ, handāhaṃ yaṃ me bhagavā nagarakaṃ upanissāya viharanto ekaṃ kathaṃ kathesi, taṃ sāremi, evaṃ me bhagavā suññatākathaṃ kathessatī’’ ti dasabalaṃ sārento ekamidan tiādimāha. "
686882,132,432,2,6,1,30,4,Tattha idan ti nipātamattameva. 
686883,132,432,7,49,1,276,33,"Kaccimetaṃ, {bhante}ti thero ekapade ṭhatvā saṭṭhipadasahassāni uggahetvā dhāretuṃ samattho, kiṃ so‘‘ suññatāvihārenā’’ ti ekaṃ padaṃ dhāretuṃ na sakkhissati, sotukāmena pana jānantena viya pucchituṃ na vaṭṭati, pākaṭaṃ katvā vitthāriyamānaṃ suññatākathaṃ sotukāmo ajānanto viya evamāha. "
686884,132,432,50,73,1,142,17,"Eko ajānantopi jānanto viya hoti, thero evarūpaṃ kohaññaṃ kiṃ karissati, attano jānanaṭṭhānepi bhagavato apacitiṃ dassetvā‘‘ kaccimetan’’ tiādimāha. "
686885,132,433,2,8,1,61,5,{Pubbepī}ti paṭhamabodhiyaṃ nagarakaṃ upanissāya viharaṇakālepi. 
686886,132,433,9,12,1,19,2,{Etarahipī}ti idānipi. 
686887,132,433,13,17,1,23,4,Evaṃ pana vatvā cintesi–
686888,132,433,18,55,1,177,23,"‘‘ ānando suññatākathaṃ sotukāmo, eko pana sotuṃ sakkoti, na uggahetuṃ, eko sotumpi uggahetumpi sakkoti, na kathetuṃ, ānando pana sotumpi sakkoti uggahetumpi kathetumpi,( kathemissa) suññatākathan’’ ti. "
686889,132,433,56,61,1,36,4,Iti taṃ kathento {seyyathāpī}tiādimāha. 
686890,132,433,62,102,1,411,32,"Tattha suñño {hatthigavāssavaḷavenā}ti tattha kaṭṭharūpapotthakarūpacittarūpavasena katā hatthiādayo atthi, vessavaṇamandhātādīnaṃ ṭhitaṭṭhāne cittakammavasena katampi, ratanaparikkhatānaṃ vātapānadvārabandhamañcapīṭhādīnaṃ vasena saṇṭhitampi, jiṇṇapaṭisaṅkharaṇatthaṃ ṭhapitampi jātarūparajataṃ atthi, kaṭṭharūpādivasena katā dhammasavanapañhapucchanādivasena āgacchantā ca itthipurisāpi atthi, tasmā na so tehi suñño. "
686891,132,433,103,117,1,170,12,"Indriyabaddhānaṃ saviññāṇakānaṃ hatthiādīnaṃ, icchiticchitakkhaṇe paribhuñjitabbassa jātarūparajatassa, nibaddhavāsaṃ vasantānaṃ itthipurisānañca abhāvaṃ sandhāyetaṃ vuttaṃ. "
686892,132,434,2,25,1,219,21,"Bhikkhusaṅghaṃ {paṭiccā}ti bhikkhūsu hi piṇḍāya paviṭṭhesupi vihārabhattaṃ sādiyantehi bhikkhūhi ceva gilānagilānupaṭṭhākauddesacīvarakammapasutādīhi ca bhikkhūhi so asuññova hoti, iti niccampi bhikkhūnaṃ atthitāya evamāha. "
686893,132,434,26,34,1,49,7,"Ekattan ti ekabhāvaṃ, ekaṃ asuññataṃ atthīti attho. "
686894,132,434,35,40,1,35,5,Eko asuññabhāvo atthīti vuttaṃ hoti. 
686895,132,434,41,47,1,57,5,{Amanasikaritvā}ti citte akatvā anāvajjitvā apaccavekkhitvā. 
686896,132,434,48,57,1,73,9,Gāmasaññan ti gāmoti pavattavasena vā kilesavasena vā uppannaṃ gāmasaññaṃ. 
686897,132,434,58,61,1,27,3,Manussasaññāyapi eseva nayo. 
686898,132,434,62,87,1,167,22,"Araññasaññaṃ paṭicca manasi karoti ekattan ti idaṃ araññaṃ, ayaṃ rukkho, ayaṃ pabbato, ayaṃ nīlobhāso vanasaṇḍoti evaṃ ekaṃ araññaṃyeva paṭicca araññasaññaṃ manasi karoti. "
686899,132,434,88,91,1,21,2,{Pakkhandatī}ti otarati. 
686900,132,434,92,96,1,32,3,{Adhimuccatī}ti evanti adhimuccati. 
686901,132,434,97,116,1,118,17,"Ye assu {darathā}ti ye ca pavattadarathā vā kilesadarathā vā gāmasaññaṃ paṭicca bhaveyyuṃ, te idha araññasaññāya na santi. "
686902,132,434,117,120,1,23,3,Dutiyapadepi eseva nayo. 
686903,132,434,121,132,1,90,11,Atthi cevāyan ti ayaṃ pana ekaṃ araññasaññaṃ paṭicca uppajjamānā pavattadarathamattā atthi. 
686904,132,435,2,22,1,171,17,"Yañhi kho tattha na {hotī}ti yaṃ migāramātupāsāde hatthiādayo viya imissā araññasaññāya gāmasaññāmanussasaññāvasena uppajjamānaṃ pavattadarathakilesadarathajātaṃ, taṃ na hoti. "
686905,132,435,23,37,1,127,14,Yaṃ pana tattha avasiṭṭhan ti yaṃ migāramātupāsāde bhikkhusaṅgho viya tattha araññasaññāya pavattadarathamattaṃ avasiṭṭhaṃ hoti. 
