687844,132,639,2,12,1,91,10,Evaṃ pavattasallāpasseva tassa janassa candamaṇḍalaṃ ohāya taṃ cakkaratanaṃ abhimukhaṃ hoti. 
687845,132,639,13,28,1,63,11,Tato tehi‘‘ kassa nu kho idaṃ nibbattan’’ ti vutte bhavanti vattāro–
687846,132,639,29,45,1,80,10,"‘‘ na kassaci aññassa, nanu amhākaṃ rājā pūritacakkavattivatto, tassetaṃ nibbattan’’ ti. "
687847,132,639,46,59,1,72,11,"Atha so ca mahājano, yo ca añño passati, sabbo cakkaratanameva anugacchati. "
687848,132,639,60,91,1,283,29,"Tampi cakkaratanaṃ raññoyeva atthāya attano āgatabhāvaṃ ñāpetukāmaṃ viya sattakkhattuṃ pākāramatthakeneva nagaraṃ anusaṃyāyitvā rañño antepuraṃ padakkhiṇaṃ katvā antepurassa uttarasīhapañjaraāsanne ṭhāne yathā gandhapupphādīhi sukhena sakkā hoti pūjetuṃ, evaṃ akkhāhataṃ viya tiṭṭhati. "
687849,132,640,2,17,1,169,15,Evaṃ ṭhitassa panassa vātapānacchiddādīhi pavisitvā nānāvirāgaratanappabhāsamujjalaṃ anto pāsādaṃ alaṅkurumānaṃ pabhāsamūhaṃ disvā dassanatthāya sañjātābhilāso rājā hoti. 
687850,132,640,18,23,1,60,5,Parijanopissa piyavacanapābhatena āgantvā tamatthaṃ nivedeti. 
687851,132,640,24,47,1,165,18,Atha rājā balavapītipāmojjaphuṭasarīro pallaṅkaṃ mocetvā uṭṭhāyāsanā sīhapañjarasamīpaṃ gantvā taṃ cakkaratanaṃ disvā‘‘ sutaṃ kho pana metan’’ tiādikaṃ cintanaṃ cintesi. 
