687863,132,642,36,59,1,169,17,"Rājayuttā pana janasaṅgahatthaṃ nagaravīthīsu bheriyo carāpenti‘‘ tātā amhākaṃ rañño cakkaratanaṃ nibbattaṃ, attano attano vibhavānurūpena maṇḍitappasādhitā sannipatathā’’ ti. "
