688009,132,685,2,54,1,309,37,"263. Paṭhamaṃ devadūtaṃ {samanuyuñjitvā}ti ettha daharakumāro atthato evaṃ vadati nāma‘‘ passatha, bho, mayhampi tumhākaṃ viya hatthapādā atthi, sake panamhi muttakarīse palipanno, attano dhammatāya uṭṭhahitvā nhāyituṃ na sakkomi, ahaṃ kiliṭṭhagattomhi, nhāpetha manti vattumpi na sakkomi, jātitomhi aparimuttatāya ediso jāto. "
