688012,132,685,82,91,1,64,8,"Tenesa devadūto nāma jāto, vacanattho pana maghadevasutte vuttova. "
688013,132,686,2,12,1,68,9,Dutiyaṃ devadūtan ti etthāpi jarājiṇṇasatto atthato evaṃ vadati nāma–
