688651,132,847,2,57,1,409,47,So sāsanaṃ sutvā amaccādayo sannipatantūti bheriṃ carāpetvā nagaramajjhe amaccādiparivuto setacchattena dhāriyamānena pallaṅkavare nisinno lañchanaṃ bhinditvā vatthaṃ apanetvā samuggaṃ vivaritvā anto bhaṇḍikaṃ muñcitvā lākhāguḷe disvā‘‘ mayhaṃ sahāyo pukkusāti‘ jutavittako me sahāyo’ ti maññamāno maññe imaṃ paṇṇākāraṃ pahiṇī’’ ti ekaṃ guḷaṃ gahetvā hatthena vaṭṭetvā tulayantova anto dussabhaṇḍikaṃ atthīti aññāsi. 
688652,132,847,58,79,1,155,19,"Atha naṃ pallaṅkapāde paharitvā tāvadeva lākhā paripati, so nakhena karaṇḍakaṃ vivaritvā anto kambalaratanaṃ disvā itarepi vivarāpesi, sabbepi kambalā ahesuṃ. "
688653,132,847,80,92,1,100,11,"Atha ne pattharāpesi, te vaṇṇasampannā phassasampannā dīghato soḷasahatthā tiriyaṃ aṭṭhahatthā ahesuṃ. "
688654,132,847,93,101,1,49,6,"Mahājano disvā aṅguliyo poṭhesi, celukkhepaṃ akāsi,–"
688655,132,847,102,122,1,120,15,"‘‘ amhākaṃ rañño adiṭṭhasahāyo pukkusāti adisvāva evarūpaṃ paṇṇākāraṃ pesesi, yuttaṃ evarūpaṃ mittaṃ kātun’’ ti attamano ahosi. "
688656,132,847,123,131,1,53,7,"Rājā ekamekaṃ kambalaṃ agghāpesi, sabbe anagghā ahesuṃ. "
688657,132,847,132,141,1,64,8,"Tesu cattāro sammāsambuddhassa pesesi, cattāro attano ghare akāsi. "
688658,132,847,142,144,1,12,2,Tato cintesi–
688659,132,847,145,169,1,129,18,"‘‘ pacchā pesentena paṭhamaṃ pesitapaṇṇākārato atirekaṃ pesetuṃ vaṭṭati, sahāyena ca me anaggho paṇṇākāro pesito, kiṃ nu kho pesemī’’ ti? "
688660,132,848,2,9,1,47,7,Kiṃ pana rājagahe tato adhikaṃ ratanaṃ natthīti? 
688661,132,848,10,32,1,145,19,"No natthi, mahāpuñño rājā, apica kho panassa sotāpannakālato paṭṭhāya ṭhapetvā tīṇi ratanāni aññaṃ ratanaṃ somanassaṃ janetuṃ samatthaṃ nāma natthi . "
688662,132,848,33,43,1,77,9,So ratanaṃ vicinituṃ āraddho– ratanaṃ nāma saviññāṇakaṃ aviññāṇakanti duvidhaṃ. 
688663,132,848,44,50,1,62,5,"Tattha aviññāṇakaṃ suvaṇṇarajatādi, saviññāṇakaṃ indriyabaddhaṃ. "
688664,132,848,51,63,1,107,11,"Aviññāṇakaṃ saviññāṇakasseva alaṅkārādivasena paribhogaṃ hoti, iti imesu dvīsu ratanesu saviññāṇakaṃ seṭṭhaṃ. "
688665,132,848,64,68,1,58,4,Saviññāṇakampi duvidhaṃ tiracchānaratanaṃ manussaratananti. 
688666,132,848,69,84,1,128,12,"Tattha tiracchānaratanaṃ hatthiassaratanaṃ, tampi manussānaṃ upabhogatthameva nibbattati , iti imesupi dvīsu manussaratanaṃ seṭṭhaṃ. "
688667,132,848,85,89,1,54,4,Manussaratanampi duvidhaṃ itthiratanaṃ purisaratananti. 
688668,132,848,90,97,1,71,7,Tattha cakkavattino rañño uppannaṃ itthiratanampi purisasseva upabhogaṃ. 
688669,132,848,98,103,1,42,5,Iti imesupi dvīsu purisaratanameva seṭṭhaṃ. 
688670,132,849,2,6,1,58,4,Purisaratanampi duvidhaṃ agāriyaratanaṃ anagāriyaratanañca. 
688671,132,849,7,21,1,135,12,"Tattha agāriyaratanesupi cakkavattirājā ajja pabbajitasāmaṇeraṃ pañcapatiṭṭhitena vandati, iti imesupi dvīsu anagāriyaratanameva seṭṭhaṃ. "
688672,132,849,22,26,1,60,4,Anagāriyaratanampi duvidhaṃ sekkharatanañca asekkharatanañca. 
688673,132,849,27,40,1,106,12,"Tattha satasahassampi sekkhānaṃ asekkhassa padesaṃ na pāpuṇāti, iti imesupi dvīsu asekkharatanameva seṭṭhaṃ. "
688674,132,849,41,45,1,44,4,Tampi duvidhaṃ buddharatanaṃ sāvakaratananti. 
