688678,132,850,21,27,1,57,6,Sadevakasmiñhi loke buddharatanasamaṃ ratanaṃ nāma natthi. 
688679,132,850,28,37,1,86,9,Tasmā asadisameva ratanaṃ mayhaṃ sahāyassa pesessāmīti cintetvā takkasīlavāsino pucchi–
688680,132,850,38,53,1,77,11,‘‘ tātā tumhākaṃ janapade buddho dhammo saṅghoti imāni tīṇi ratanāni dissantī’’ ti. 
688681,132,850,54,64,1,59,9,"Ghosopi so mahārāja tāva tattha natthi, dassanaṃ pana kutoti."
688682,132,851,2,12,1,36,7,‘ ‘ Sundaraṃ tātā’’ ti rājā tuṭṭho cintesi–
688683,132,851,13,32,1,144,15,"‘‘ sakkā bhaveyya janasaṅgahatthāya mayhaṃ sahāyassa vasanaṭṭhānaṃ sammāsambuddhaṃ pesetuṃ, buddhā pana paccantimesu janapadesu na aruṇaṃ uṭṭhapenti. "
688684,132,851,33,38,1,30,5,Tasmā satthārā gantuṃ na sakkā. 
