688734,132,873,91,102,1,105,11,Atha taṃ samuggaṃ vivaritvā rājalañchanaṃ bhinditvā sukhumakambalaṃ ubhato viyūhitvā suvaṇṇapaṭṭaṃ addasa. 
688735,132,874,2,6,1,16,3,So taṃ pasāretvā–
