689211,132,953,67,95,1,204,26,"Atha vā panassa vihāre vā āsanasālāya vā nisinnassa upāsakā pattaṃ ādāya attano gharaṃ gantvā khādanīyabhojanīyaṃ pakkhipanti, tasmiṃ khaṇe tassa maggavuṭṭhānaṃ hoti, idampi dānaṃ maggasamaṅgino dinnaṃ nāma. "
689212,132,953,96,106,1,105,9,Tattha soṇḍiyaṃ udakassa viya sotāpattiphalasacchikiriyāya paṭipanne dinnadānassa asaṅkhyeyyatā veditabbā. 
689213,132,953,107,119,1,117,12,Tāsu tāsu mahānadīsu mahāsamudde ca udakassa viya sotāpannādīsu dinnadānassa uttaritaravasena asaṅkhyeyyatā veditabbā. 
689214,132,953,120,132,1,115,12,Pathaviyā khayamaṇḍalamatte padese paṃsuṃ ādiṃ katvā yāva mahāpathaviyā paṃsuno appameyyatāyapi ayamattho dīpetabbo. 
689215,132,954,2,12,1,31,5,380. Satta kho {panimā}ti kasmā ārabhi?
689216,132,954,13,45,1,173,26,"‘‘ Saṅghe gotami dehi, saṅghe te dinne ahañceva pūjito bhavissāmi saṅgho cā’’ ti hi vuttaṃ, tattha sattasu ṭhānesu dinnadānaṃ saṅghe dinnaṃ nāma hotīti dassetuṃ imaṃ desanaṃ ārabhi. "
689217,132,954,46,64,1,145,15,"Tattha buddhappamukhe {ubhatosaṅghe}ti ekato bhikkhusaṅgho, ekato bhikkhunisaṅgho, satthā majjhe nisinno hotīti ayaṃ buddhappamukho ubhatosaṅgho nāma. "
689218,132,954,65,74,1,64,8,Ayaṃ {paṭhamā}ti imāya dakkhiṇāya samappamāṇā dakkhiṇā nāma natthi. 
689219,132,954,75,81,1,57,6,Dutiyadakkhiṇādayo pana etaṃ paramadakkhiṇaṃ na pāpuṇanti. 
689220,132,955,2,12,1,84,9,Kiṃ pana tathāgate parinibbute buddhappamukhassa ubhatosaṅghassa dānaṃ dātuṃ sakkāti? 
689221,132,955,13,14,1,5,1,Sakkā. 
689222,132,955,15,16,1,6,1,Kathaṃ? 
689223,132,955,17,43,1,220,25,"Ubhatosaṅghassa hi pamukhe sadhātukaṃ paṭimaṃ āsane ṭhapetvā ādhārakaṃ ṭhapetvā dakkhiṇodakaṃ ādiṃ katvā sabbaṃ satthu paṭhamaṃ datvā ubhatosaṅghassa dātabbaṃ, evaṃ buddhappamukhassa ubhatosaṅghassa dānaṃ dinnaṃ nāma hoti. "
689224,132,955,44,52,1,43,7,"Tattha yaṃ satthu dinnaṃ, taṃ kiṃ kātabbanti? "
689225,132,955,53,61,1,61,7,"Yo satthāraṃ paṭijaggati vattasampanno bhikkhu, tassa dātabbaṃ. "
689226,132,955,62,80,1,141,15,"Pitusantakañhi puttassa pāpuṇāti, bhikkhusaṅghassa dātumpi vaṭṭati, sappitelāni pana gahetvā dīpā jalitabbā, sāṭakaṃ gahetvā paṭākā āropetabbāti. "
689227,132,955,81,85,1,47,2,{Bhikkhusaṅghe}ti aparicchinnakamahābhikkhusaṅghe. 
689228,132,955,86,89,1,28,3,Bhikkhunisaṅghepi eseva nayo. 
689229,132,956,2,9,1,66,5,"{Gotrabhuno}ti gottamattakameva anubhavamānā, nāmamattasamaṇāti attho. "
689230,132,956,10,13,1,33,2,{Kāsāvakaṇṭhā}ti kāsāvakaṇṭhanāmakā. 
689231,132,956,14,25,1,69,10,Te kira ekaṃ kāsāvakhaṇḍaṃ hatthe vā gīvāya vā bandhitvā vicarissanti . 
689232,132,956,26,34,1,84,8,Gharadvāraṃ pana tesaṃ puttabhariyā kasivaṇijjādikammāni ca pākatikāneva bhavissanti. 
689233,132,956,35,46,1,80,10,Tesu dussīlesu saṅghaṃ uddissa dānaṃ {dassantī}ti ettha dussīlasaṅghanti na vuttaṃ. 
689234,132,956,47,52,1,29,5,Saṅgho hi dussīlo nāma natthi. 
689235,132,956,53,64,1,90,11,Dussīlā pana upāsakā tesu dussīlesu bhikkhusaṅghaṃ uddissa saṅghassa demāti dānaṃ dassanti. 
689236,132,956,65,73,1,85,8,Iti bhagavatā buddhappamukhe saṅghe dinnadakkhiṇāpi guṇasaṅkhāya asaṅkhyeyyāti vuttaṃ. 
689237,132,956,74,79,1,69,5,Kāsāvakaṇṭhasaṅghe dinnadakkhiṇāpi guṇasaṅkhāyeva asaṅkhyeyyāti vuttā. 
689238,132,956,80,94,1,98,13,"Saṅghagatā dakkhiṇā hi saṅghe cittīkāraṃ kātuṃ sakkontassa hoti, saṅghe pana cittīkāro dukkaro hoti. "
689239,132,957,2,12,1,77,9,"Yo hi saṅghagataṃ dakkhiṇaṃ dassāmīti deyyadhammaṃ paṭiyādetvā vihāraṃ gantvā,–"
689240,132,957,13,47,1,160,23,"‘‘ bhante, saṅghaṃ uddissa ekaṃ theraṃ dethā’’ ti vadati, atha saṅghato sāmaṇeraṃ labhitvā‘‘ sāmaṇero me laddho’’ ti aññathattaṃ āpajjati, tassa dakkhiṇā saṅghagatā na hoti. "
689241,132,957,48,62,1,82,10,Mahātheraṃ labhitvāpi‘‘ mahāthero me laddho’’ ti somanassaṃ uppādentassāpi na hotiyeva. 
689242,132,957,63,94,1,208,30,"Yo pana sāmaṇeraṃ vā upasampannaṃ vā daharaṃ vā theraṃ vā bālaṃ vā paṇḍitaṃ vā yaṃkiñci saṅghato labhitvā nibbematiko hutvā saṅghassa demīti saṅghe cittīkāraṃ kātuṃ sakkoti, tassa dakkhiṇā saṅghagatā nāma hoti. "
689243,132,957,95,100,1,35,4,Parasamuddavāsino kira evaṃ karonti. 
689244,132,958,2,22,1,113,15,Tattha hi eko vihārasāmi kuṭumbiko‘‘ saṅghagataṃ dakkhiṇaṃ dassāmī’’ ti saṅghato uddisitvā ekaṃ bhikkhuṃ dethāti yāci. 
689245,132,958,23,48,1,234,25,So ekaṃ dussīlabhikkhuṃ labhitvā nisinnaṭṭhānaṃ opuñjāpetvā āsanaṃ paññāpetvā upari vitānaṃ bandhitvā gandhadhūmapupphehi pūjetvā pāde dhovitvā telena makkhetvā buddhassa nipaccakāraṃ karonto viya saṅghe cittīkārena deyyadhammaṃ adāsi. 
689246,132,958,49,70,1,137,16,"So bhikkhu pacchābhattaṃ vihārajagganatthāya kudālakaṃ dethāti gharadvāraṃ āgato, upāsako nisinnova kudālaṃ pādena khipitvā‘‘ gaṇhā’’ ti adāsi. "
