689256,132,959,41,45,1,32,4,Tena teneva samayena kathetabbaṃ. 
689257,132,959,46,60,1,144,13,"Saṅghato uddisitvā gahitasamaṇaputhujjano hi pāṭipuggaliko sotāpanno, saṅghe cittīkāraṃ kātuṃ sakkontassa puthujjanasamaṇe dinnaṃ mahapphalataraṃ. "
689258,132,959,61,68,1,71,7,Uddisitvā gahito sotāpanno pāṭipuggaliko sakadāgāmītiādīsupi eseva nayo. 
