689260,132,959,83,121,1,169,25,"Yaṃ pana vuttaṃ‘‘ sīlavato kho, mahārāja, dinnaṃ mahapphalaṃ, no tathā dussīle’’ ti, taṃ imaṃ nayaṃ pahāya‘‘ catasso kho imānanda, dakkhiṇā visuddhiyo’’ ti imasmiṃ catukke daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
689261,132,960,2,15,1,74,7,"381. Dāyakato {visujjhatī}ti mahapphalabhāvena visujjhati, mahapphalā hotīti attho. "
