689265,132,961,2,9,1,76,5,Paṭiggāhakato {visujjhatī}ti ettha kalyāṇīnadīmukhadvāravāsikevaṭṭo kathetabbo. 
689266,132,961,10,29,1,139,15,So kira dīghasomattherassa tikkhattumpi piṇḍapātaṃ datvā maraṇamañce nipanno‘‘ ayyassa maṃ dīghasomattherassa dinnapiṇḍapāto uddharatī’’ ti āha. 
