689301,132,975,56,66,1,59,8,Na cakkhuṃ {upādiyissāmī}ti cakkhuṃ tīhi gāhehi na gaṇhissāmi. 
689302,132,975,67,78,1,80,11,Na ca me cakkhunissitaṃ viññāṇan ti viññāṇañcāpi me cakkhunissitaṃ na bhavissati. 
