689317,132,978,2,13,1,96,10,Apicāyaṃ upāsako dānādhimutto dānābhirato buddhānaṃ santikaṃ gacchanto tucchahattho na gatapubbo. 
689318,132,978,14,22,1,93,7,"Purebhattaṃ gacchanto yāgukhajjakādīni gāhāpetvā gacchati, pacchābhattaṃ sappimadhuphāṇitādīni. "
