689326,132,979,2,8,1,45,5,Yena bhagavā {tenupasaṅkamī}ti kasmā upasaṅkami? 
689327,132,979,9,19,1,135,10,Tusitabhavane kirassa nibbattamattasseva tigāvutappamāṇaṃ suvaṇṇakkhandhaṃ viya vijjotamānaṃ attabhāvaṃ uyyānavimānādisampattiñca disvā–
689328,132,979,20,79,1,372,48,"‘‘ mahatī ayaṃ mayhaṃ sampatti, kiṃ nu kho me manussapathe kammaṃ katan’’ ti olokento tīsu ratanesu adhikāraṃ disvā cintesi‘‘ pamādaṭṭhānamidaṃ devattaṃ nāma, imāya hi me sampattiyā modamānassa satisammosopi siyā, handāhaṃ gantvā mama jetavanassa ceva bhikkhusaṅghassa ca tathāgatassa ca ariyamaggassa ca sāriputtattherassa ca vaṇṇaṃ kathetvā tato āgantvā sampattiṃ anubhavissāmī’’ ti. "
