689991,133,65,45,49,1,47,4,Sutan ti savanayogena purimacakkadvayasampattiṃ. 
689992,133,65,50,58,1,74,8,Na hi appatirūpadese vasato sappurisūpanissayavirahitassa vā savanaṃ atthi. 
689993,133,65,59,75,1,172,13,"Iccassa pacchimacakkadvayasiddhiyā āsayasuddhi siddhā hoti, purimacakkadvayasiddhiyā payogasuddhi, tāya ca āsayasuddhiyā adhigamabyattisiddhi, payogasuddhiyā āgamabyattisiddhi. "
689994,133,65,76,103,1,228,25,"Iti payogāsayasuddhassa āgamādhigamasampannassa vacanaṃ aruṇuggaṃ viya sūriyassa udayato, yoniso manasikāro viya ca kusalakammassa, arahati bhagavato vacanassa pubbaṅgamaṃ bhavitunti ṭhāne nidānaṃ ṭhapento evaṃ me sutan tiādimāha. "
689995,133,66,2,13,1,120,10,Aparo nayo– evan ti iminā nānappakārapaṭivedhadīpakena vacanena attano atthapaṭibhānapaṭisambhidāsampattisabbhāvaṃ dīpeti. 
689996,133,66,14,19,1,87,5,Sutan ti iminā sotabbabhedapaṭivedhadīpakena dhammaniruttipaṭisambhidāsampattisabbhāvaṃ. 
689997,133,66,20,27,1,56,7,Evan ti ca idaṃ yoniso manasikāradīpakavacanaṃ bhāsamāno–
689998,133,66,28,40,1,65,8,‘‘ ete mayā dhammā manasānupekkhitā diṭṭhiyā suppaṭividdhā’’ ti dīpeti. 
689999,133,66,41,46,1,47,5,Sutan ti idaṃ savanayogadīpakavacanaṃ bhāsamāno–
690000,133,66,47,60,1,53,9,‘‘ bahū mayā dhammā sutā dhātā vacasā paricitā’’ ti dīpeti. 
